### Get all books
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books

### Add a new book - Book 1
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "title": "Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone",
  "author": "J.K. Rowling",
  "price": 19.99
}

